==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wend
<hw>Wend</hw> <pr>(w⟦ecr⟧nd)</pr>, <mark>obs.</mark> <def><pos>p.
p.</pos> of <er>Wene</er>.</def> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
